contents.P:
The purpose of this part is to establish agency procedures which supplement NEPA regulations issued by CEQ and USDA. This regulation, together with such NEPA regulations issued by CEQ and USDA, will supersede regulations issued by the Farm Service Agency (FSA) on December 20, 1974 (
39 FR 43996
).

P.text:
 Conduct any studies which are deemed necessary and appropriate by
FSA to determine the impact of the proposed action on the human
environment;
